}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "HUB_FE1.1_ZL7", "VERSION:0.1", "DATE:2010.06.30", and "MAKE PY SHENZHEN HEXING" <!-- yes, it says that --> is silkscreened on the board.
This particular device has "USB2.0 7port HUB" text on the top of the hub. There are two ports on the top and four ports on the rear. The remaining port is on the left side - the host connection and barrel plug are on the right.
This device presents itself to the host as two 1a40:0101 devices.
The '''Sabrent''' USB-HWPS may be this device. It looks essentially identical.. minus slight cosmetic differences.
